---

<Layout 
  title="Christopher J. Bradley | Gulf War Veteran, Love Advocate, Civic Educator"
  description="Gulf War veteran and civic educator teaching liberty principles to families. Creator of educational platforms focused on American founding principles, family unity, and intentional living. Love everyone, start with you."
>
  <Navigation />

  <main id="main-content">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-liberty-cream/30 to-white dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-950">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-24">
        <div class="text-center animate-fade-in">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-liberty-navy dark:text-slate-100 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
            Christopher J. Bradley
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-liberty-navy/80 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Gulf War Veteran, Lawyer, Love Advocate, Family Court Reform Activist
          </p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-liberty-navy/70 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Teaching liberty principles to families. Spreading the message: Love everyone, start with you.
          </p>
          
          <!-- Featured Projects Quick Links -->
          <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
            {featuredProjects.map((project) => (
              <a
                href={project.url}
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 rounded-lg border-2 border-liberty-navy/20 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white/80 dark:bg-slate-900/80 hover:border-liberty-gold hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
                rel="noopener"
              >
                <span class="text-2xl" aria-hidden="true">{project.icon}</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-liberty-navy dark:text-slate-100">{project.name}</span>
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Core Message Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-slate-950">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-liberty-navy dark:text-slate-100 mb-6">
            The Greatest Lesson
          </h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
            <p class="text-liberty-navy/80 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              For most of the last decade, I lived on a sailboat along the northwest gulf coast of Florida.
              I photographed over 2,000 sunsets in the same sacred space and learned the greatest lesson:
              Life is simple, love everyone and start with you.
            </p>
            <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-liberty-gold pl-4 italic text-xl my-8">
              What if you are the person we are all waiting on?
            </blockquote>
            <p class="text-liberty-navy/80 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              We could all live in peace on this earth if each of us simply made peace with every person we know.
              If we each decided to love everyone, it would be game over - love wins.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Projects Ecosystem Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-liberty-cream/10 to-white dark:from-slate-900/30 dark:to-slate-950">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-liberty-navy dark:text-slate-100 mb-4">
            A Connected Ecosystem
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-liberty-navy/70 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            I've created 9 platforms that work together to support families, educators, and citizens. 
            Each serves a unique purpose ‚Äî from teaching constitutional principles to children, 
            to providing tools for mindful living, to analyzing legislation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value Props Grid -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
          <div class="text-center p-6">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üìö</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-liberty-navy dark:text-slate-100 mb-2">Education</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-liberty-navy/70 dark:text-slate-400">
              Teaching liberty principles and civic engagement to the next generation
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üë®‚Äçüë©‚Äçüëß‚Äçüë¶</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-liberty-navy dark:text-slate-100 mb-2">Family Unity</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-liberty-navy/70 dark:text-slate-400">
              Tools and resources for strengthening family bonds and preserving memories
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">‚öñÔ∏è</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-liberty-navy dark:text-slate-100 mb-2">Civic Engagement</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-liberty-navy/70 dark:text-slate-400">
              Understanding government, analyzing legislation, and advocating for reform
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <a
            href="/projects"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border border-transparent text-lg font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-gradient-liberty hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
            aria-label="Explore all Christopher's projects"
          >
            Explore All 9 Projects
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-liberty-cream/20 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-liberty-navy dark:text-slate-100 mb-4">
          Ready to Learn More?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-liberty-navy/70 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6">
          Discover the full story behind the platforms and the mission
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
          <a
            href="/about"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-gradient-liberty hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
            aria-label="Learn more about Christopher"
          >
            About Christopher
          </a>
          <a
            href="/projects"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-liberty-navy text-base font-medium rounded-md text-liberty-navy dark:text-slate-100 dark:border-slate-300 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 hover:bg-liberty-navy hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-all duration-300"
            aria-label="View all projects with descriptions"
          >
            View All Projects
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <FooterEnhanced />
</Layout>
